  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15059">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 4. </span>
      <b>Classic Experiments.</b> Do TWO of the following: <br /><i
        >Resource:</i
      >
      <a
